Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.09,0:01:34.51,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Distant Thunder (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't that a downer?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like you're going over there\Nto strangle an old, senile dog.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.71,0:02:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It kind of makes you worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought in a situation like this,\Nmaybe you're the type to throw the match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.35,0:02:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're such a nice guy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shouichi Matsunaga, 7th dan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}65 years old.\NFrom Fukushima Prefecture.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He became a professional at 25 years old,\Nso he has 40 years of experience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At his best, he was in Rank B-1 for one term.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've spotted him many times at the Shogi Hall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I saw the back of a small statured man\Nwho always walked briskly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sendagaya Station
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This scenery for 40 years...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Forty years."\NI said it out loud, but I couldn't imagine it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's over twice as long as I've been alive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.45,0:03:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}On this 81-square board,\Nhe's lived and died over and over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Matsunaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear if Mr. Matsunaga is demoted to C-2,\Nhe'll finally retire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forty years... An overwhelming span of time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder how he feels right now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.44,0:03:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't imagine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,God, to be honest, I just want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But please somehow let me win!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clap-clap. And so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ehhh?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.08,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gong
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's how he feels?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}True, I didn't imagine that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now he's drawing a fortune paper!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he's incredibly agitated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What did it say?\NOh no, he looks super depressed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You shouldn't even draw a fortune slip\Nat a time like this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I should go! I need to get to the table,\Ncalm down, and wait for him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.11,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like\Nhe saw something\Nhe shouldn't have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So... um...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Matsunaga isn't here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.00,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thump\NThump
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}D-Don't tell me he really did go home...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.75,0:05:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's here! What a relief.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He stopped?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's not moving?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-He moved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Psychological warfare?\NSome kind of veteran player strategy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, how will he play?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.29,0:05:40.17,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forty years...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What will my life be like in 40 years?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.52,0:06:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}5-c-Silver General?\NThe Bear in the Castle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Surrounds himself, and then\Nhe means to have a long, careful battle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I'll go with 1-e-Pawn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That keeps the king pinned down\Nso I can attack whenever I need to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}7-d-Pawn. A sudden attack?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's not doing Bear in the Castle?\NI can't tell what his strategy is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Hmph!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I'll...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.32,0:06:50.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}1-b-Lance?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.99,0:06:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? So he's doing\NBear in the Castle after all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Upsy daisy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Continue\NOperation{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't tell. What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Moving the pieces randomly?\NNo, there's no way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think he's just trying to confuse me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He has some kind of plan, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The calm mind is the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}White Side\NMatsunaga 7th-Dan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shuffle shuffle. Phew.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The bear goes in!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, it's in there. Then here I go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.18,0:07:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}7-e-Pawn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did he just make a weird noise?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What expression is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Tea
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Bishop... Um... Knight...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait a minute, he wasn't thinking about it?\NNo countermeasure against 7-e-Pawn?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Pawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.45,0:07:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I can see someone behind him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So 3-b-Silver General?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now Mino Castle?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Thump
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, 7-g-Knight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5}Matsunaga 7th-Dan\N...2-b-King
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, it's coming out?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please stay there!\NIf you move now, you'll be in trouble, Mr. Bear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:13.16,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eeeek!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.83,0:08:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-This is painful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.87,0:08:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For some reason, it's very painful.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes. The king and rook are in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's true.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if I place the bishop there,\Nhe'll match it at 5-e, and then a 3-f-Knight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, that is dubious...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...but I've still got the upper hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shoot! If he takes my rook...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Glance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Glance"? What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he luring me in? Is he babbling?\NHiding his true intentions? But his acting is bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:09:01.29,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Too much\NToo much
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:09:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Th-This is painful.\NThis is seriously painful for some reason.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never felt like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would be difficult to lose on purpose,\Neven if I wanted to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}E-Enough. Let's finish this. Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It kind of makes you worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're such a nice guy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm really sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Such a nice guy, such a nice guy,\Nsuch a nice guy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.85,0:09:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm grateful you said that about me, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't think I'm nice at all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.56,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga 7th-Dan appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:26.56,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Player: Kiriyama
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.94,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga 7th-Dan appears!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.94,RightSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight Strategy\NEscape Items
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry! I'm from the\Npressure-free generation, with no patience!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.69,DefaultLeftH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Player: Kiriyama
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:29.69,DefaultLow2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Choose a strategy\NTake Care of Your Life    Let's Go Go Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.69,0:09:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's Go Go Attack
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:34.45,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}I'm really sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}And so, 15 Minutes Later
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:42.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Clatter\NClatter
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.87,DefaultRightH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi players\Nmust never do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wh-What a bad attitude!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.25,0:09:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where's the dignity of 40 years\Nof professional shogi?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean, even as a human being,\Nwhat is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you sure you want to go out this way?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At least, make me respect you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enough. Hurry! Let's hurry and go home!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to wait together\Nfor the elevator with him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so I'll dash down the stairs!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Gasp
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Apparently was thinking the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trip
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.86,0:10:14.49,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ba-Bam
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.49,0:10:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eek, Mr. Matsunaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look okay? I nearly died!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get you to a doctor. I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.12,0:10:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D-Doctor? I don't like doctors!\NIt was just a small trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you youngsters are so pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you said you nearly died!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop whining.\NGo, already! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see your face—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Gr-Gr-Gr-Gr
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Treat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Treat me to soba! No, grilled eel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you just told me to "get lost"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.57,0:10:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:11:00.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The deluxe meal!\NYou've got the money, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.99,Next Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Distant Thunder (Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:39.01,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Distant Thunder (Part 3)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious! This aroma! The famous\NMr. Miyanogawa does not disappoint!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:12:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}4,720 yen (2 Layer Deluxe Meal)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot and tender to the core!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}2,100 yen (Standard Meal on Bamboo)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, kid?\NYour first time eating eel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna be first-class,\Nyou gotta start by eating first-class food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:10.58,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heh-Heh
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.58,0:13:11.79,RightSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chew\NChew
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.37,0:13:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am paying for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Miyanogawa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez. Don't be such a stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single drop of emotion.\NYou're ruining the taste of my beer! Grr.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kouda is your foster parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.43,0:13:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was also a prize pupil, really strong,\Nbut no personality whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, he's got that daughter, too.\NA real "darling".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strong-willed,\Nwith a face as beautiful as the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.53,0:13:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she's pretty scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When she becomes an adult, just you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She'll become a poisonous woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.33,0:13:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Living under a roof with that kind of person,\NI bet you got tormented by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, y'know, all women are scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.88,0:14:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should meet my wife, sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Splashy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Shudder\NShudder\NShudder
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That scary?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bad topic. It's makin' the booze go bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Excuse me!\NSake! The sake menu, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Drinks
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Fukushima- Soul of Aizu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They've got Soul of Aizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know about Soul of Aizu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's sake from my hometown, Aizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It smells great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tokyoites say people from Fukushima
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are "stubborn" and "too serious".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But we're aware of our surroundings\Nand emphasize etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're clueless\Nabout the soul of the true Fukushima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:38.12,LeftSign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:41.63,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shouichi\NMatsunaga
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back to the year 1643.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The third Tokugawa shogun, Iemitsu
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,recognized a minor feudal lord\Nwith just 30,000 koku
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for his shrewdness and stern honesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was granted an extremely generous\N230,000 koku and became
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Masayuki Hoshina
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the first-generation feudal lord of Aizu.\NThat was Masayuki Hoshina.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was a truly wise ruler!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Masayuki was not only an administrator,\Nbut was made the adjunct
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to the fourth Tokugawa shogun, Ietsuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As the center of the shogunate administration,\Nhe set forth a number of policies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.11,0:15:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Tamagawa\NWater Supply
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In order to provide the residents of Edo\Nwith drinking water,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he created the Tamagawa\Nwater supply river works.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To prevent neighboring dwellings\Nfrom burning in a fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ueno\NMain Streets
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.75,0:15:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he widened streets from six to ten ken, and\Nestablished main streets in Ueno as a firebreak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When a plan to rebuild the tower\Nof the burnt down Edo Castle came up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he rejected it. "Peace reigns in the land, so it's\Nunnecessary. No need to waste expenditures!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How decisive! How manly!\NHe's the pride of Aizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And do you know the "pension system"?\NIt's said Masayuki devised that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To prepare for a famine, he laid down a law
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,stating that rice be stored in granaries\Nas well as distributed for free to elderly people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,aged 90 or older, whatever their social status.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that our pension system today\Nis based on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Masayuki, who stressed welfare of the people,\Nhad a spirit flowing with genuine benevolence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that even now supports the sincere hearts\Nof Fukushima Prefecture citizens today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it, young'un?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's leap forward 250 years,\Nto the Boshin War...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Y-You're continuing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:13.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, I'll have another Soul of Aizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what was I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. My grandson's name is Kousuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.86,0:16:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and boy is he a handful...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}Wait a second!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:26.23,LeftSignM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zu-bang
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}What happened to the Boshin War?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:29.86,DefaultLow,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still a child, so not accustomed to the behaviors of a drunk
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\i1}What happened to the talk\Nabout the souls of people from Fukushima?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Eel Miyanogawa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}That Legendary Thing\N(souvenir)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}All right, let's go to the next place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wobble\NWobble
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a drunk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's the exact image of a drunk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just say "another place"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going home!\NBesides, I'm out of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! What kind of winner says\N"I'm going home" first?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay for the next one.\NI know just the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stagger
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Limp
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.82,0:17:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.61,0:17:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch where you walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seems the booze\Ngoes straight to my legs these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His arm is so thin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The arm of a man who's grasped\Nnothing but shogi pieces for 40 years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.76,0:17:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear Mr. Matsunaga will finally retire.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling I couldn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:18:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling I wouldn't be able to win at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I thought about on the way to the hall was\N"How can I look cool losing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You probably didn't know me,\Nbut I know a lot about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're the fifth middle school student\Nwho became a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've held fast to the shogi board for 40 years\Nwithout any records to show for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.60,0:18:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so to me, your existence\Nwas something bright and frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.65,0:18:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I could only think of you as the Grim Reaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come to close the curtain\Non my life as a shogi player.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was frightened of you, and then\Ndisgusted with myself for feeling that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:19:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then, the instant I saw you\Nsitting up straight in the match room,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.76,0:19:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.60,0:19:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Such a young, beautiful Grim Reaper."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you would.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.24,0:19:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If someone was going to close the curtain,\NI couldn't ask for anyone better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I would at least fight fair and square\Nonce more before fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet... Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...something inside of me began to struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't want to die!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here I was at the end of my long career,\Nmuddying my legacy, struggling pathetically,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and one thought welled up from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"I don't want to lose."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Even still, I don't want to lose."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.11,0:19:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was my crazed line of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Matsunaga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like shogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I win, I'd be so happy,\Nthat I'd want to shout with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I lose, it's agonizing, like somebody\Ntrampled my innards with muddy boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.14,0:20:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel tormented, from everyone saying\Nthat I don't deserve to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, I couldn't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can I even express it in words?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd be depressed,\Nso I thought I could cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.23,0:21:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard. You won today, right?\NIt can't be helped. It's a match, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.07,0:21:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Matsunaga isn't going to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to keep playing shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rei. Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.72,0:21:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.30,0:21:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.77,0:21:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Would you help me convince\Nmy wife and daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That I've decided not to retire after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.73,0:22:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They must be worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.32,0:22:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shogi players do need physical strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I don't want to quit. If I do quit...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.78,0:22:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}...I can't act big at home anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.12,0:22:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All this time, I've never helped with chores,\Nsaying I needed to focus on shogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I quit now, I know exactly\Nhow my family will take their revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? That's the reason?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.34,0:22:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My blood runs cold just thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hahaha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So from now on, you're doing\Nyour share of the housework.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't wait to train you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Heeheehee!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dad, give Kou a bath!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hahahaha
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Heeheehee
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.98,0:22:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}Gaga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The horror! They'll make me wash dishes\Nand my grandson, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's wash them! Both!\NDon't wait until you retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.78,0:22:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.32,0:22:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say "I don't wanna!"\NFamily members should help each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to teach you how to do chores?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna! I don't wanna! I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what anyone says, I definitely
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.54,0:22:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,don't wanna!
