Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.01,0:24:35.31,EpNum,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 10
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.55,0:24:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When did it start?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.51,0:24:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When did Christmas\Nbecome painful for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.81,0:24:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad, can I open it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.85,0:24:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A Game Bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.73,0:24:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.11,0:24:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which would be more fitting\Nfor their last Christmas together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.15,0:24:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"March Comes in Like a Lion."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.91,0:24:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You won't watch it next time?\NExcuse me? That's impossible.
